ygData.messageBody:
Everstomped + EQ'Lizer

The best part of Everstomped is to state down ya race/class/body part, and
it will give u the items available for you. For eg, u dunno want is the
better 1H slash for your wood elf bard, you can check the site for the
dam/delay list.

Once you get the name of the item that you want, you can check EQ'lizer for
the location of spawn (some dun have location but more than half got).

Everstomped:
http://eq.stomped.com/

EQ'Lizer:
http://gameznet.com/eq/

Happy camping ;)
